The repository contains source and compiled files presented in the book:
      Methods and tools for computer-aided design of multidimensional filters in signal processing, //www.vitalsource.com/en-uk
in the papers:
      Cariow A., Naumowicz M., Handkiewicz A., Structure and Principles of Operation of a Quaternion
      VLSI Multiplier, Appl. Sci. 2024, 14(18), 8123; https://doi.org/10.3390/app14188123
      A. Handkiewicz, G. Krzywoszyja, W. Zajac, M. Naumowicz, Filter design based on multi-port and multi-dimensional gC circuit, 
      Circuits, Systems, and Signal Processing, https://doi.org/10.1007/s00034-025-03004-0
and in the paper to be published:
      Current-Mode Circuit Design for NSFET Technology
